{"tid":617131,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［造福大眾］餵白鴿，有冇人知佢地鍾意食咩？","createTime":"2018-04-04T18:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T09:52:48.000Z","uid":100347,"like":7,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"12f7d4a42c9f081d06f81197cebab2a4cda62735","tid":617131,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:13:54.000Z","msg":"蟲就冇，暫時只有麵包同八年前新年嘅嘉頓紅罐雜餅<br />\n<br />\n發夢見到每日只有早上六時餵<br />\n<br />\n窗外嘅少少牆位可以被佢地企，撒少少食物。<br />\n<br />\n對上少少半空嘅地方會有一條60cm大麻繩<br />\n<br />\n每日睇心情喺一個地方搽膠水<br />\n<br />\n班撚雀搶完食完會飛走，剩低一兩隻一直叫<br />\n<br />\n每日慳到一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花園試過一個鍋蓋加支棍撐起，繩都唔需要，隻雀撞跌支棍就byebye。如果細隻就放走，大隻就拎去食同賣羽毛，後來堆雀開始唔過來，而家鍾意拉橫條繩，自由改位置，fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dc4867d8f0854c4a87ed23526224676253d889","tid":617131,"uid":35870,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:23:15.000Z","msg":"初初唔知樓主up乜9，1999<br />\n跟住睇下睇下咩慳得一餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927b483ed7736d6caad6a073fb196433cbbc05fb","tid":617131,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"屌你啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae76649d015bb95051822a195ebd552f48ab7195","tid":617131,"uid":61748,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p